The material was amber, known to the Greeks as elektron. Funnily enough they posited that this might be a type of magnetism like the lodestones, but rejected the idea as amber attracted non metallic objects. 2 millennia later we learnt electromagnetism is a single force. https://t.co/7CtEvns4aj
